GoodHire,focuses,on,background,checks,solutions,to,hire,potential,employees,It,targets,start,ups,mid,size,companies,and,enterprises,The,API,allows,integration,of,employment,background,checks,into,web,applications,This,API,can,be,accessed,via,HTTPS,with,GET,and,POST,methods,To,authenticate,developers,use,HTTP,basic,auth,to,obtain,a,key,with,username,and,password,Includes,resources,to,add,company,report,order,partner,access,consent,upload,and,report,status,For,support,contact,api,goodhire,com